text: The 7th annual Isthmus Beer and Cheese Fest will take place Saturday, January 16th, 2016 from 2-6 pm at the Alliant Energy Center in Madison. Tickets go on sale October 1st. more » ISTHMUS LIVE SESSIONS Isthmus Live Sessions: Dessa She may be the lone female member of Minneapolis hip-hop collective Doomtree, but that’s not all that makes Dessa stand out.
